 ency: Scheduled several times per year.\n\n• Notes: The market often r
 eacts not only to the rate decision\, but also to the statement\, foreca
 sts\, press conference and tone.\n\n• Acronyms: FOMC = Federal Open Ma
 rket Committee\; RBA = Reserve Bank of Australia.\n\nOfficial source: ht
