SUMMARY:🔥 AU ABS: Consumer Price Index\, Australia\, August 2026
DESCRIPTION:Source: AU ABS\nImpact: high\nSource: AU ABS\nImpact: high\nS
 ource: AU ABS\nImpact: high\nSource: AU ABS\nImpact: high\nSource: AU AB
 S\nImpact: high\nSource: AU ABS\nImpact: high\nOfficial ABS series page 
 release date. Time zone shown by ABS: AEST.\n\nExplainer:\n• What it i
 s: Consumer Price Index\n\n• Measures: Change in the prices paid by co
 nsumers for a basket of goods and services.\n\n• Usual market effect: 
 Higher-than-forecast inflation is usually bullish for the local currency
  and bearish for bonds\, because markets may price in higher interest ra
 tes.\n\n• Why traders care: CPI is one of the most watched inflation i
 ndicators because it can quickly shift central-bank rate expectations.\n
 \n• Frequency: US CPI is monthly. Australian CPI has both monthly indi
 cator releases and quarterly CPI releases.\n\n• Notes: Core CPI remove
 s volatile items such as food and energy to give a cleaner read on under
 lying inflation pressure.\n\n• Acronyms: CPI = Consumer Price Index.\n
 \nOfficial source: https://www.abs.gov.au/statistics/economy/price-index
 es-and-inflation/consumer-price-index-australia\n\nExplainer:\n• What 
 it is: Consumer Price Index\n\n• Measures: Change in the prices paid b
 y consumers for a basket of goods and services.\n\n• Usual market effe
 ct: Higher-than-forecast inflation is usually bullish for the local curr
 ency and bearish for bonds\, because markets may price in higher interes
 t rates.\n\n• Why traders care: CPI is one of the most watched inflati
 on indicators because it can quickly shift central-bank rate expectation
 s.\n\n• Frequency: US CPI is monthly. Australian CPI has both monthly 
 indicator releases and quarterly CPI releases.\n\n• Notes: Core CPI re
 moves volatile items such as food and energy to give a cleaner read on u
 nderlying inflation pressure.\n\n• Acronyms: CPI = Consumer Price Inde
 x.\n\nOfficial source: https://www.abs.gov.au/statistics/economy/price-i
 ndexes-and-inflation/consumer-price-index-australia\n\nExplainer:\n• W
 hat it is: Consumer Price Index\n\n• Measures: Change in the prices pa
